properties.areaDesc: Waters from Point Arena to Point Reyes 10-60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 31 at 2:05AM PST until February 1 at 9:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the first Small Craft Advisory, seas 10 to 11 feet
at 15 seconds. For the second Small Craft Advisory, seas
around 10 feet at 13 seconds expected.

* WHERE...Waters from Point Arena to Point Reyes 10-60 NM.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 10 AM PST this
morning. For the Small Craft Advisory, from 3 PM to 9 PM PST
Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM PST THIS MORNING... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 PM TO 9 PM PST SATURDAY
